to let it all go,

00:01:48.462 --> 00:01:54.009 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But at times,
it comes back to mind.

00:01:54.009 --> 00:02:00.557 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I wish I could put
all this behind.

00:02:00.557 --> 00:02:07.022 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
